PURPOSE
  Bash script for start/stop/restart/status check of TrinityCore servers.

STATUS
  Working as of: https://github.com/TrinityCore/TrinityCore/commit/5365bd25fae59a6ae225534b779bd6c14779599a

DETAILS
  This script allows an administrator to start, stop, restart, or check
  the running status of multiple TrinityCore servers. By default it is
  configured to support two server binaries named "authserver" and
  "worldserver".

INSTALL
  01 : Open trinitycore-server.sh in a text editor and modify all
       config values at the top of the file.
  02 : Optionally modify the output messages below the config values.
  03 : Use and enjoy.


